{"tid":1379454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我喺到宣布，唔好再塞地鐵！因為我要準時番工！","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T19:49:19.000Z","uid":284263,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed961ca917a92de068fdc4010d23294816abc5b9","tid":1379454,"uid":284263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"平時番工已經好鬼迫！<br />\n<br />\n門A有人夾到袋，閂唔到門。好啦無事企入啲。<br />\n<br />\n跟住第2卡有人夾到公事包，又打番開車門！好啦，你以為閂到門喇咩？<br />\n<br />\n月台嘅人見到開左門，喺第3卡衝門迫入黎啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要係咁 loop ⋯<br />\n<br />\n仆街！我駛鬼你做大龍鳳喺金鐘不合作咩！<br />\n你自己又比警察拉！又阻住哂我番工！<br />\n<br />\n跟本地鐵平時日日都有人不合作！只不過係無人知佢地係邊個咋！"},{"pid":"3766d5cf3f6f48d8dfa019d3e381bb2662961dcd","tid":1379454,"uid":284263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:32:03.000Z","msg":"仲要每一個站都係咁⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦而家，一塞啲市民就知你不合作！<br />\n<br />\n唔駛做大龍鳳比人拉架！"},{"pid":"9ae7cde0c18629ea7263a2f2f9e883c468596652","tid":1379454,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/28154834/9ee87159.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2F28154834%2F9ee87159.jpg&h=d27305e7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}